        <title>Software Note</title>
        <p>The algorithms described in this work will be available in the academic software SPM8, which can be downloaded from <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.fil.ion.ucl.ac.uk/spm/">http://www.fil.ion.ucl.ac.uk/spm/</ext-link>.</p>
      </sec>
